Class Restaurant

java.lang.Object
hr.java.restaurant.model.Restaurant
public class Restaurant extends Object
Represents a restaurant in the system, containing details such as its name, address, available meals, and the personnel (chefs, waiters, deliverers) working at the restaurant.

    • Restaurant

      public Restaurant(String name, Address address, Meal[] meals, Chef[] chefs, Waiter[] waiters, Deliverer[] deliverers)
      Constructs a new Restaurant with the specified name, address, meals, chefs, waiters, and deliverers.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the restaurant.
      address - the address of the restaurant.
      meals - an array of meals offered by the restaurant.
      chefs - an array of chefs working at the restaurant.
      waiters - an array of waiters working at the restaurant.
      deliverers - an array of deliverers employed by the restaurant.
